-*- mode: org -*-

Gloa is an academic article management program written in Guile Scheme.
It is intended to closely inter-operate with GNU Emacs.

* Requirements
   * GNU Guile >= 3.0

* Building
#+begin_src sh
$ ./bootstrap && ./configure && make
#+end_src

